---

<section id="about" class="w-full py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-base/50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative group" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/20 to-accent/20 rounded-2xl blur-2xl group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-500 opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="relative aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-tertiary/20 shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/61719180?v=4"
            alt="Jhonatan Mizu Profile"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-base_alt border border-tertiary/20 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hidden md:block">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold text-xl">4+</div>
              <div>
                 <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Years of</p>
                 <p class="text-fontColor/60 text-xs">Experience</p>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div data-aos="fade-left">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
          About <span class="text-primary">Me</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-fontColor text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Hello, I'm <span class="text-white font-bold">Jhonatan Mizu</span>. 👋
        </p>
        <p class="text-fontColor/80 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg">
          I'm a versatile <span class="text-primary font-medium">FullStack Developer</span> and UI/UX design enthusiast with over 4 years of professional experience crafting digital experiences that bridge the gap between complex engineering and intuitive design.
        </p>
        <p class="text-fontColor/80 leading-relaxed mb-8 text-lg">
          My approach combines technical rigor with a deep understanding of user behavior. I specialize in building scalable, performant applications using modern stacks like <span class="text-white">React, Node.js, and Python</span>, always keeping the user at the center of every architectural decision.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
           <div class="bg-base_alt/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-tertiary/10">
              <h4 class="text-primary font-bold mb-1">Architecture</h4>
              <p class="text-fontColor/60 text-sm">Clean code & scalability</p>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-base_alt/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-tertiary/10">
              <h4 class="text-primary font-bold mb-1">UI/UX Design</h4>
              <p class="text-fontColor/60 text-sm">User-centric interfaces</p>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
